INSERT INTO `article` VALUES ('37', '众里寻她千百度，蓦然回首，那景却在，延京深谷处', '众里,寻她千,百度,蓦然,回首,那景,却在,延京,深谷,北京', '北京再次被雾霾笼罩的上周末，有一群来自百度ECOM的汉子、妹子与沐雨户外一同体会了最美的北京金秋，呼吸到了十月最新鲜的空气。 ', '', '<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 29.4px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(244, 244, 244);\">北京再次被雾霾笼罩的上周末，有一群来自百度ECOM的汉子、妹子与沐雨户外一同体会了最美的北京金秋，呼吸到了十月最新鲜的空气。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 29.4px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(244, 244, 244);\">金秋，十月，是北京最美的季节。环京赛、北京马拉松赛、鸟幻音乐节……各种聚会扎堆儿报道，更有重阳登高、香山赏红叶、植物园菊花展、银杏林留影的，大家都不想错过色彩绚丽的秋天。位于北京西北的延庆，依旧用它迷人的秋色吸引着各方朋友。</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 29.4px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(244, 244, 244);\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 29.4px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(244, 244, 244);\"/><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 29.4px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(244, 244, 244);\">这次沐雨户外为百度骑友推荐的是龙庆峡至小铺村的香龙路－延琉路经典骑行线路，香龙路也是全国职业自行车公路赛的训练赛段。期间可欣赏到各色的风景，还可欣赏到延庆大力推广的四季花海。路面平整，全程略有缓坡起伏。小声说一句，俱乐部为大家准备的是一水儿的TREK哟！！</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 29.4px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(244, 244, 244);\"/><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 29.4px; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(244, 244, 244);\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 25px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 29.4px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(244, 244, 244);\">蓝天白云在北京市区已经多日不见，可就在距离北京市区不到两小时车程的延庆区，这天有多蓝，空气有多纯净，无法描述，上片为证 （文：沐雨户外 图：百度沈俊杰＋沐雨户外）</p><p><br/></p>', '20170917\\2f275d998868df67234be031dc2d5f8f.jpg', '2', '1', '36', null, '1505623511', '1505618320', '0', '1');
